      <div class="block__content">
      <div><div class="view view-post-roll-promotion view-id-post_roll_promotion view-display-id-block_2 js-view-dom-id-83098f88d5f86b7e89311fe6face53e5e1e6d89102385258db46a24a0aa65d5f">
  
    
      
      <div class="view-content">
          <div class="views-row"><div class="views-field views-field-field-body"><div class="field-content"><div class="native-ad"><div class="native-img"><a href="https://gardenplanner.almanac.com/?utm_source=ofa_web&amp;utm_medium=web&amp;utm_campaign=text_ad&amp;utm_content=text_ad" target="_blank"><img src="https://www.almanac.com/sites/default/files/houseads/garden-planner-native-2025-purple.png" alt="Almanac Garden Planner" width="200" height="143" loading="lazy"></a></div><div class="native-text"><p><strong>The Almanac Garden Planner - Use It Free for 7&nbsp;Days!</strong></p><p>Plan your 2025 garden with our award-winning Garden&nbsp;Planner.</p><p><a class="text-button" href="https://gardenplanner.almanac.com/?utm_source=ofa_web&amp;utm_medium=web&amp;utm_campaign=text_ad&amp;utm_content=text_ad">Try&nbsp;Now</a></p></div></div></div></div></div>

