    <h2 class="field__label">Cooking Notes</h2>
              <div class="field__item"><p>Lettuce makes the perfect base for any number of salads. Try <a href="https://www.almanac.com/content/eight-great-salad-recipes">these eight great salad recipes</a> with your&nbsp;harvest!</p></div>
